    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chutney is cooking, drain and rinse the <strong>chickpeas</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>drained chickpeas</strong> to a baking tray with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong>, <strong>half</strong> the <strong>curry powder</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray in the oven for 10-15 min or until crisp – these are your <strong>crispy curried chickpeas</strong></p>",
