    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>carrot</strong> <strong>&</strong> <strong>cabbage slaw mix</strong> to a large bowl with the <strong>sliced shallot</strong>, <strong>cider vinegar</strong>, <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong> and <strong>chopped mint</strong></p><p>Season with a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and 1/2 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> and mix it all together – this is your <strong>ginger</strong> <strong>slaw</strong></p>",
